 735                        else

 0742                    }
 0743                }
 0744            }

 1549        private static object FindSubObject(object o, string path)
 01550        {
 01551            if (path == null)
 01552            {
 01553                return o;
 1554            }
 1555
 01556            object result = o;
 1557
 01558            foreach (string pathElement in path.Split('.'))
 01559            {
 01560                Type type = result.GetType();
 1561
 01562                Regex regex = new Regex(@"(\w+)\[(\d+)\]$");
 01563                Match match = regex.Match(pathElement);
 01564                int index = -1;
 01565                string fieldName = pathElement;
 1566
 01567                if (match.Success)
 01568                {
 01569                    fieldName = match.Groups[1].Value;
 01570                    index = int.Parse(match.Groups[2].Value);
 01571                }
 1572
 01573                FieldInfo field = type.GetField(fieldName, DefaultBindingFlags);
 1574
 01575                if (field == null)
 01576                {
 01577                    return null;
 1578                }
 1579
 01580                result = field.GetValue(result);
 1581
 01582                if (index >= 0)
 01583                {
 01584                    System.Collections.IEnumerable enumerable = result as System.Collections.IEnumerable;
 1585
 01586                    result = null;
 1587
 01588                    if (enumerable != null)
 01589                    {
 01590                        int i = 0;
 1591
 01592                        foreach (object obj in enumerable)
 01593                        {
 01594                            if (index == i)
 01595                            {
 01596                                result = obj;
 01597                                break;
 1598                            }
 01599                            i++;
 01600                        }
 01601                    }
 01602                }
 1603
 01604                if (result == null)
 01605                {
 01606                    return null;
 1607                }
 01608            }
 1609
 01610            return result;
 01611        }
